      "widgets_values": [
        "A highly detailed, cozy isometric illustration of a stylized miniature bathroom, enclosed within a decorative rounded room frame. The art style is defined by thick, clean, bold black outlines and a soft pastel color palette. The perspective is a consistent, high isometric view. All shapes are simple, charming, and detailed with minimal complex shading. The entire scene has a warm, Lo-Fi Cozy atmosphere.\n\nThe walls feature warm paneling with decorative vertical lines. The floor has checkered tiles with a simple geometric pattern. The lighting is soft diffused natural light from a small window.\n\nIn the center of the room, a prominent clawfoot bathtub with wooden feet and a plank tray holding a ceramic cup and a candle. On the left wall, a multi-level wooden shelf holds stacked towels, cosmetic bottles, and decorative jars, with fluffy slippers below. On the right wall, a wooden vanity cabinet with small legs, a sink basin, chrome faucet, and a rounded mirror with a flower accent above.\n\nSmall details like a potted plant with large broad leaves, a frog-shaped bath mat with a small crown complete the scene. No watermarks."
      ],
      "color": "#232",
      "bgcolor": "#353"
    },
